00:26:14.600 --> 00:26:26.320
If you take a marshmallow, you know it's about
an inch tall, maybe half an inch wide.

00:26:26.320 --> 00:26:38.150
So from that, I can calculate the volume of
the marshmallow.

00:26:38.150 --> 00:26:46.280
Just by taking an inch by half-an-inch by
